schema.description:
Newline-delimited SSE frames. Each frame contains an `event:` line with the event name and a `data:` line with the JSON-encoded event payload. Example frame:

  event: service.ready
  data: {"event":"service.ready","node":"legion-01","timestamp":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z"}

schema.example:
event: service.ready
data: {"event":"service.ready","node":"legion-01","timestamp":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z"}

event: extension.loaded
data: {"event":"extension.loaded","name":"lex-node","node":"legion-01","timestamp":"2026-03-22T12:00:01Z"}
